#, php-format
msgid "Please ensure that you copy the full secret key when generating a new Stripe API key and not just the visible characters in your %1$sStripe dashboard%2$s. Alternatively, you can revoke the existing secret key and generate a new one. For detailed instructions, please refer to %3$sStripe's API keys documentation%4$s."
